### HEALTH CHECK - VERIFY THE WALLET SERVICE IS RUNNING
GET http://localhost:4002/health

### CREATE WALLET - OPEN A WALLET FOR THE TEST PLAYER
POST http://localhost:4002/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-rmq-1",
  "currency": "BRL"
}

### GET WALLET - CHECK INITIAL BALANCE AND WALLET DATA
GET http://localhost:4002/wallets/player-rmq-1

### DEBIT BET - SIMULATE GAME SERVICE DEBITING A PLACED BET
POST http://localhost:4002/wallets/debit-bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-rmq-1",
  "operationId": "operation-rmq-debit-1",
  "amountCents": "100",
  "referenceRoundId": "round-rmq-1",
  "referenceBetId": "bet-rmq-1"
}

### GET WALLET - CHECK BALANCE AFTER BET DEBIT
GET http://localhost:4002/wallets/player-rmq-1

### CREDIT CASHOUT - SIMULATE GAME SERVICE PAYING A SUCCESSFUL CASHOUT
POST http://localhost:4002/wallets/credit-cashout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-rmq-1",
  "operationId": "operation-rmq-credit-1",
  "amountCents": "1000",
  "referenceRoundId": "round-rmq-1",
  "referenceBetId": "bet-rmq-1"
}

### GET WALLET - CHECK BALANCE AFTER CASHOUT CREDIT
GET http://localhost:4002/wallets/player-rmq-1
